This paper proposes a mechanism for generating vector embeddings of time series that exhibit resilience to warping, which is applicable in learning tasks that require kernel or vectors. Therefore, the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), information retrieval (cs.IR), and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
